 the setting.\\\"\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1057, \"end\": 1074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7759436594867625e-32, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Butorganizers\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"Sundaythat Jolly\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"inspiration\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"the setting\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The production team's admission of drawing inspiration from Da Vinci's famous painting of the Last Supper should dispel the notion that the ceremony was devoid of Christian symbolism.\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1178, \"end\": 1186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.4463114404258e-46, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 1281, \"end\": 1300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_symbolism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0945828879541974e-24, \"text\": \"Christian symbolism\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_symbolism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_symbolism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The production team's admission\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"inspiration\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"the notion\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This acknowledgment directly counters the claims that it had no connection to Jesus and Christianity.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999951208884226, \"rank\": 4.879135218765264e-06, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 1390, \"end\": 1402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999920546476511, \"rank\": 7.945415685249376e-06, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This acknowledgment\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"the claims\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1350}, {\"ngram\": \"no connection\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Furthermore, images or paintings of Bacchanalian feasts bear no resemblance to the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1441, \"end\": 1453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bacchanalia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9621700663730219e-59, \"text\": \"Bacchanalian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bacchanalia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bacchanalia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"images\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1424}, {\"ngram\": \"paintings\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"no resemblance\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To see an actual image of a Bacchanalian feast, go to thislink.\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1529, \"end\": 1541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bacchanalia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9621700663730219e-59, \"text\": \"Bacchanalian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re