ems\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2269}, {\"ngram\": \"1 John\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This profound promise symbolizes intimate fellowship and victory for believers, reflecting their triumph over worldly influences.\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This profound promise\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"intimate fellowship\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2340}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"believers\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"their triumph\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2392}, {\"ngram\": \"worldly influences\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rev.\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rev.\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"3:20-21: \\\"Behold, I stand at the door and knock.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If anyone hears my voice and opens the door, I will come in to him and eat with him, and he with me.\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2573, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"my voice\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The one who conquers, I will grant him to sit with me on my throne, as I also conquered and sat down with my Father on his throne.\\\"\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2705, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my throne\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2640}, {\"ngram\": \"my Father\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"his throne\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Church fathers like Irenaeus of Lyon, Cyril of Jerusalem, Athanasius, John Chrysostom, Augustine of Hippo, and Maximus the Confessor connected the Eucharist to the eventual spiritual re